profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

Techno Kitchen Refacing is an Ontario based kitchen renovation company that specializes in refacing, rather than replacing. Recently, we brought on another member to the team to supply the increasing demand. Now, we can serve you faster, and across a larger area.

Techno's word-of-mouth marketing philosophy shows how happy customers have been with the product. Honesty and customer satisfaction are of the utmost concern for Techno and the customer will benefit every time.

Want to see it for yourself? Our customers are so happy and enthusiastic about the work that they've allowed us to invite you into their homes to see firsthand the quality of the work. Call today and ask how to arrange a meeting with Frank.

profile:
For 25 years, Canlik has been the premier Kitchen Refacing Specialist in Greater Toronto Area. It's kitchen upgrade solutions are custom to fit individual family needs, New Kitchens or Refacing Kitchens, they are more personal, flexible, affordable and environmental friendly. Since 1990, Canlik’s principal has been the same – delivering high quality products and services. No pushy sales. Consultants focus on providing honest and unbiased suggestions so that home owners can make the right decisions. Kitchen projects can be overwhelming and confusing – but it does not have to be if customers chose Canlik Kitchens. 
 
Details on our solutions: - 
 
(A) Kitchen Refacing,
Canlik’s very popular "Premier Kitchen Refacing” aims at delivering custom kitchen looks with fraction of the cost. It uses the existing infrastructure and replaces exterior elements, like the cabinet doors, gable and fillers. It reduces wastage and helps avoid hidden costs. Kitchen Refacing solution has been providing great alternatives for those who want to achieve their renovation goals with less effort, less risk and have their budget under control.
 
(B) Custom New Kitchens 
“Canlik Custom Kitchens” allow home owners fully utilize limited spaces because cabinets are custom built to fit spaces. It can handle challenging space issues that "Modular kitchens" can hardly address. It also makes preserving the existing layouts and the foot prints possible, so that the flooring and other elements are not affected. Storage efficiency is achieved by detail oriented cabinet configurations design and adding effective accessories, if necessary.

Reclaim your kitchen cabinets, vanities, and woodwork!

We believe in doing things right the first time. We specialize in the fine art of cabinet refinishing, painting, re-spraying and wood finishing. profile:
MacLeans Custom Kitchens is family owned and operated.

All of Macleans Custom Kitchens reviews are authentic, unedited, and written directly by our customer.

We design quality Kitchens and handle complete renovations from floor to ceiling. 

In the early 1990's, brothers Terry and Dave MacLean, second generation cabinet builders, opened their showroom/workshop in Pickering, making the move to Bowmanville in 2004.

Macleans Custom Kitchens offers one stop shopping with 6 different kitchen displays in our showroom and a huge selection of colours and door styles for your kitchen or vanity. We have a large selection of ceramic tile, granite, quartz and laminate samples.

As part of our free estimate service, from measurements taken at your home, we offer computer assisted designs. We can produce a floor plan and 3D images that can be viewed in our showroom. Written estimates are free to take home.

Whether we custom build, or order your cabinets from one of carefully selected, Canadian suppliers, we guarantee only the finest quality products and workmanship and generous warranties. Rip-out, disposal and installation and all necessary, plumbing, electrical and appliance hook-ups are all included in our pricing - there are no surprises.

Each project is done by or closely overseen by the owners personally. From start to finish, your renovation is our top priority, and we will work within your busy schedule to complete the job in a timely fashion. 


Our business has been built on word-of-mouth referrals and repeat customers, based on our solid practical knowledge, honesty, experience and courteous service. We look forward to being able to add you to our list of satisfied customers!

Our services include:
Full Service Kitchen Renoations
*Custom Cabinets
*Made to Order Cabinets and Vanities- cash and carry for your installation
*Ceramic Tile


*Granite / Quartz Countertops

profile:
Bathroom Renovation, Kitchen Renovation, Basement Renovation

Our process begins in the comfort of your home with a complimentary consultation. A qualified renovator will take you through our virtual gallery showing off hundreds of inspirational ideas featuring real kitchen & bathroom renovations we have completed, or are capable of offering. Have something else in mind? Splendid! We are sleuths at sourcing hard-to-find products. Together, we’ll discover functional solutions and fashionable options that suit your tastes. Once this process is complete, we’ll present you with a quote and a comprehensive plan encompassing the layout, products and details of your renovation.

As soon as you give us the green light to begin your project, we will prepare a detailed contract and a comfortable payment schedule.Then you can sit back and leave the rest to us! One of our Project Managers will coordinate with our team of skilled drywallers, carpenters, plumbers and electricians so that your dream kitchen or bathroom renovation runs smoothly. In our experience, dealing with one person is much easier for you and ensures the job is done right – the first time!

During the renovation process, rest assured we will treat your home as if it was our own. From drop sheets to vent filters, we’ll create a “bubble” around the project area to keep the space clean with minimal disruption to your household. Upon completion of the project, a cleaning crew will ensure your new kitchen or bathroom is pristine – ready to enjoy immediately – and for years to come.

For added peace of mind, we are proud to guarantee all our Toronto kitchen and bathroom renovation work for 5 years. That’s our commitment and it’s what makes the Kitchen & Bath Guys the definitive choice for discriminating homeowners… like you!

profile:
Why choose The Renovators of Canada?  
 
For over the past 20 years our focus on customer experience has helped The Renovators of Canada grow to locations in Durham, Aurora, Stouffville, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, Hamilton, Guelph, Kitchener, Waterloo, Barrie, Oshawa, Oakville and Cambridge. 
 
Unique to the industry, The Renovators of Canada provides a 10 year warranty on all craftsmanship. This home renovation warranty protection was established to provide peace of mind as home and business owners contemplate renovating a personal or commercial space. 
 
T-ROC is a fully licensed and insured including WSIB. Other affiliations include memberships with the National Kitchen and Bath Association, CARAHS, Better Business Bureau.  
 
We have a proven track record working with our customers with full transparency in every aspect of your project.  Can’t be present all the time during the renovation process?  No worries, we have specialized client software that allows you to see the entire schedule and pictures as the project happens in real time. We care for your home like it’s our own and always conduct ourselves respectfully and professionally.  
 
With our motivated and innovative professionals we will transform your house and make your dream home a reality.  Visit our website at www.trocanada.com

Capable Group 

Residential Renovations Toronto:-
 
Professional residential renovations can breathe new life into your Toronto home. Whether you are seeking renovations to just one room, the whole house, the exterior or the interior, The Able Group can provide you with everything you need from design to planning to execution, with our building supplies in Toronto.
 
Whether your renovation requirements are something very practical such as updating an outdated kitchen or whether you would like to splurge on a home theatre room for your basement, The Able Group are prepared to take care of your residential renovation needs.
 
Construction Managment:-
We have developed a very comprehensive Construction Management service that has resulted in exceptional projects for countless clients. Please take a minute to review the following information to better understand how we can reliably deliver your project on-time and on-budget.
 
Basement Renovation:-
Of all home renovations, kitchen and basement remodels offer the best financial return. But there’s a caveat with basements: the quality of the new space must match the rest of the house to warrant asking for a higher selling price.

profile:
Latitude Countertops is known for producing excellent quality Natural and Engineered Stone Countertops. Our commitment to provide top notch service has made us the largest fabricator of granite & quartz counter tops in the Toronto area.  Latitude fabricates  natural stone such as Granite and Marble from reputable suppliers. You don't need to worry about the quality of your stone, we only deal with the best. 
We work with all the leading Quartz companies such as  Caesarstone, Silestone, LG Viatera, Hanstone, Compac, and Diamastone. We will also fabricate acrylics such as Corian, Hi Macs and Staron.  
Customers can purchase their Kitchen countertops & Bathroom vanities directly or through our vast dealer network. We work with dealers all over Southern and Northeastern Ontario. To find a dealer near you check our website, as well for remnants and special offers visit our website www.latitudecountertops.com and view our blog at blog.latitudeonline.ca 
We meet the needs of our Builders, renovators and Home owners throughout Ontario.

To find a dealer close to you please visit our website.

products:
Kitchen countertops and bathroom vanity countertops and shower and tub surrounds in Natural Stone such as Granite, Marble, Quartz such as Caesarstone Quartz, LG Vitera Quartz, Silestone Quartz, Hanstone Quartz, Compac Quartz, DuPont Zodiaq, DuPont Corian, Samsung Staron, Blanco Premium Sinks and Faucets.
We also do Laundry Room countertops, Entertainment Center countertops and bars, tub surrounds, fireplace walls and Hearths.
Tables and many other Natural and Engineered stone applications.
services: Latitude works on a Guaranteed 8 -10business day turnaround from countertop template to installation.  We digitally template all Kitchen and Bathroom countertops and can do so without removing your exiting countertop.  We also provide a countertop removal and or disposal service if you need to have your existing countertop removed before the new one is installed.  Our template process will take from 30min to 1.5hours.  Following the template, we will fabricate your custom countertop and return to install it within 10 business days, guaranteed.  Installations can take from 1 to 4 hours depending on the size of the project.   We also alter existing natural stone and acrylic countertops to fit new appliances.

profile:
Brandom Kitchens and Bath Design Center has grown into a trusted brand from humble beginnings in March, 1989. What began as a small rental unit on Bloor St. in Oshawa, has grown in size and tenure to the 9,000 sq ft warehouse we design from today. Our guests and repeat clients enjoy being greeted by Cheryl or Tony, before strolling through our showroom with a refreshment to gain inspiration from our many displays showcasing new products from the countries leading suppliers. Brandom takes great pride in offering a beginning-to-end approach as a team. Our clients will never find themselves shopping sections of department stores or sourcing tradespeople. Our experience has gained the confidence of many, and results in productivity while honouring our clients schedule and budget. We enjoy every step of the renovation process, from measuring and designing the space, to installing the cabinets, flooring, reworking plumbing, safely updating electrical needs, and as needed will remove walls, counters, backsplash, and dispose of all accumulated excess.

DIY's can be enticing but renovations by inexperienced contractors or labourers can quickly become expensive and stressful. 

Once a client has agreed to partner with us, our design team will present a 3D render of the discussed vision to be approved or amended, before any work commences in your home. We bring more than fifty years of aggregate experience ensuring an enjoyable, creative experience transforming their favourite space. 
In addition to primary design, our team is present for our clients during all facets of the installation, manufacturing processes and future service. 

Our team wouldn't be complete without our in-house installers who bring the design element to life with precision and care. Our installers consistently deliver excellence while showing the utmost care for remaining flooring and furniture. Installers are available upon request to revisit the site for services if needed. (All electrical and plumbing work is performed to code standards).

We are grateful for every new and returning client for making Brandom Durham's trusted design studio.

Call Cheryl today to schedule your first appointment. Our family is looking forward to working with yours!


SERVICES INCLUDE:

-design & install cabinets
-supply & install countertops
-supply & install backsplash
-supply & install flooring
-supply all plumbing needs for your project
-use certified electricians for your project
-wall removals when necessary
-remove all associated garbage

profile:
We are a manufacturer of all cabinetry components including kitchens, vanities, wall units, laundry etc.  We provide a free design/measure consultation.  We provide a full kitchen renovation service including wall removal, beam installation, flooring, lighting, trim, etc.  We have a designer on staff as well as in-house cabinetry installers and tradespeople.  
All of our cabinetry comes put together and you are welcome to purchase for your own installation or have us install it for you.  We are able to provide any door finish in any style of door as well as custom trim work, hood vents, floating shelves etc. We can supply all types of countertops including laminate, quartz, granite and butcher block. profile: RIGHT CHOICE RENOS was founded on the principles of providing honest, reliable and ethical work at a fair price specializing in Home Renovation and Electrical work. Sean D'Aguiar has over 15 years experience with dealing with various trades. Brad Emmons,owner of EMMONS ELECTRIC is a Master Electrician and ACP certified who has over 20 years experience in the industry. Together we have a combined knowledge and appreciation of the overall process and requirements to get the project completed in a time efficient manner. We understand that renovation projects can be a stressful process. We treat every project as though it is our own and hope to provide the most pleasurable experience to every customer.
services:
ACCESSIBILITY 
From design to implementation we can build accessibility ramps, decks bathrooms and more. 

BASEMENT RENOVATIONS
From start to finish we take care of the planning, demolition, wall construction, electrical work, insulation, soundproofing ceiling, drywall, door installation, new floors, painting and much more.
Separate entrance-way, In-law suites, Bedrooms, Kitchens, Playrooms, Bathrooms, Laundry Rooms and More.

CEILINGS
Upgrading your home with ceiling renovations is a surefire way of improving the quality and value of your home and will give it a new modern look. We offer installation of drop ceilings, smooth ceilings, pot-lights, coffered ceilings and more. 

DECKS
Whether you are looking to repair/refinish an existing deck or to build your dream deck we can take care of it all. From design and planning to reality.  We offer flat decks, raised decks, multi-level decks, stairways and accessible ramps and more.

DEMOLITION/CONSTRUCTION CLEANUP
As part of any renovation project demolition is always one of the first steps. we take care of all demolition and garbage removal associated.

DRYWALLING
Complete repair and refinish of existing and new drywall on walls and ceilings.

ELETRICAL
We offer fully licensed services which include complete re-wiring of existing service, knob & tube removal, aluminum wiring, trouble shooting & repairs, radiant floor heat, lighting, pool and spa Hook-ups, Panel & Service upgrades, layout and design. 

FLOORING
We can take care of all your flooring needs; from the subfloor to the installation  of carpet, tile floors, laminate or vinyl

GARAGE AND SHED CONSTRUCTION  
Need some additional storage or need some power installed? We can help by adding or upgrading an electrical service,  shelving, repairs to existing building to design and build of your new garbage, storage shed, pool house or workshop.

GARAGE DOORS
Looking to add extra space or replace that old door; We offer full Garage Builds, Door openers, Garage door upgrades, capping, interior access doors, removal and installation.

GENERAL CONTRACTING
We manage all aspects of the project from start to finish which include; design and planning, drawings, permits and inspections.

HANDYMAN SERVICES
From minor repairs to your full renovation projects, we can help with it all.  

HVAC 
Fully licensed to supply and install new furnace upgrades, fireplaces, air-conditioners, hot water tanks and on demand hot water units. 

KITCHEN RENOVATIONS
Kitchens are the heart of the home, a gathering place for family and friends to cook, eat and entertain. We provide full kitchen remodeling to simply updating your existing kitchen. We can help with the installation of cabinet lighting, new floors, pot lights or even a back-splash. 

PAINTING
We provide services for painting which include; ceilings, interior and exterior walls (brick,wood and aluminum siding), decks, sheds, fences and more.
